dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T03:47:34.000Z","msg":"一邊就150人<br />\n另一邊就叫你退休/無錢買樓就番大灣區住<br />\n司馬昭之心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00467f064579f8c8b36f6eef9da599ebee5d39cb","tid":643422,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T06:09:07.000Z","msg":"點解無 香港2047規劃？"},{"pid":"fe3784073df8c5ad627edf6063a5d8f8ef6a2f7c","tid":643422,"uid":44460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T07:01:06.000Z","msg":"正苦年年估算都錯<br />\n咁都仲有人信<br />\n<br />\n只要繼續有人信樓價只升唔跌<br />\n班鳩官繼續官商勾結<br />\nCctvb繼續日日幫地産商推樓<br />\n<br />\n出年8球上車200呎 供60年(玩埋個仔）"},{"pid":"ad538d524e213900aaa922017024481757dcb06a","tid":643422,"uid":129169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T07:05:59.000Z","msg":"150<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n認真，要夠地既話一年起碼起夠5萬個單位先夠做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}